				b Butterfly Effect
				| : 
				i At the beginning of each mystery
				| , choose one rating to receive +1 (max +3) and another to receive -1 (min -2) during this mystery. These actions disturb the spacetime and the oscillations of their characteristics is a reflection of that.
			button.sheet-broadcast-button(type='roll', name='roll_Show', value='&{template:motw-moveshare} {{CharName=@{character_name}}} {{movekey=traveler-move1}}', data-i18n-title='send_details_to_chat')
	.sheet-move
		input.sheet-checkbox(type='checkbox', name='attr_Moves-Traveler2')
		span.sheet-mainbox
		span.sheet-grayable
			span(data-i18n='traveler-move2')
				b Historian
				| : When you 
				i investigate a mystery
				|  or 
				i read a bad situation
				| , you can choose to ask \&quot;Why does this seem familiar?\&quot; as one of the questions. If possible, the Keeper will describe how a similar situation has happened in the past or future history of the world.
